data.description: 3 Bedroom and 2 Baths.  If you love Nature, this is your next Home. This Home features a great, open Floorplan with Great Room, Formal Dining Room, Eat-in Kitchen, Sun Room and more. There is a large Dining Area in the Kitchen. There are limitless possibilities with the space this Home has to offer. Inside however doesn't compare to the outside. Situated on one of the larger lots in Oliver Crossing, this Home features approximately 100' on the Little Cahaba River with a natural sitting area on the banks. Great place to waste away the afternoon relaxing after a long day. Call today for your private viewing of this immaculately kept Home.
